        </p>

        <div class="block width-max px-8 py-2 mt-8 bg-white shadow-full rounded-full text-center f5 font-josesans color-fade cursor-pointer">
          Get started<i class="ml-2 fa fa-credit-card mr-3 duration-500"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-5/12">
        <%= image_tag("svg/working.svg") %>
      </div>

    </div>

  </section>

  <section class="my-16 mx-auto w-8/12">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
      <div class="w-5/12">
        <%= image_tag("svg/business_shop.svg") %>
      </div>
      <div class="w-6/12">
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <span class="h-small w-8 bg-gray-500"></span>
          <h6 class="f6 ml-4 font-bold text-gray-500 text-uppercase">Start with us</h6>
        </div>
        <h3 class="f3 font-josesans font-bold line-height-normal">Is your site driving sales of
          <span class="text-indigo-800">business</span></h3>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-4 f7">
          We provide excellent quality digital service with tangible results measurable long-term business
        </p>
        <div class="block width-max my-8 px-8 py-2 bg-white shadow-full rounded-full text-center f5 font-josesans color-fade cursor-pointer">
          Start now <i class="ml-2 fa fa-clock mr-3 duration-500"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div>
      <h1 class="f1 text-center font-bold font-josesans">About our company</h1>
      <p class="w-1/2 mx-auto mt-4 text-center">
        We provide simple, high quality and reasonable price products for worldwide market. Driven by a strong focus on
        innovation and customer-centricity, Ecommer has quickly grown to serve over two millions customers, shoppers and
        retainers on out platform
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-16 my-16">
      <img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2015/05/15/14/22/conference-room-768441_1280.jpg" alt="" class="h-64 w-full object-cover rounded-extra-lg">
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-16 my-16">
    <div class="flex w-1/2 mx-auto">
